claim.claim-text:
1. A process for producing a patterned flexible linoleum sheet material comprising the steps of:
dispersing at least one type of linoleum particles onto at least one side of a rolled linoleum sheet; and
pressing the linoleum particles into the rolled linoleum sheet such that the linoleum particles are not substantially distorted;
cutting the rolled linoleum sheet;
rotating the rolled linoleum sheet 90°;
stacking the rolled linoleum sheet into a sheet stack; and
rolling the sheet stack into a pattern providing sheet;
